<body>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <details>
        <summary>Who can apply for a loan?</summary>
        <p>Anyone above 18 years with a valid ID and stable income can apply.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>How long does approval take?</summary>
        <p>Approval usually takes 24 to 48 hours.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>What happens if I miss a payment?</summary>
        <p>Late payments may result in penalties.</p>
    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>What documents are required?</summary>
        <p>Valid ID, proof of income, and bank statements are required.</p>
    </details>

</body>
